      *  LUC110 - Extended Narratives (Upgrade NUC002 to FBM 2.1)     *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      **
     C           LUC110    IFEQ 'Y'
      *
     C                     SETOF                     215859
      *
      ** Clear extended narratives from last record read.
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   GNAR1
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   GNAR2
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   GNAR3
      *
     C   02      STOR      CHAINXXSTDOY0             58
      *
     C   02      *IN58     IFEQ '0'
      *
      ** If Extended Narrative 1 is blank, seton 21.
     C           GNAR1     IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     MOVE '1'       *IN21
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * IF PNAR IS BLANK OUTPUT GNAR1 TO PNAR
      *
     C           GNAR1     IFNE *BLANKS
     C           PNAR      ANDEQ*BLANKS
     C                     MOVELGNAR1     PNAR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Else, if Extended Narratives record not found, seton 21.
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE '1'       *IN21
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      **
